#. §0: `axiom edgeCount_addEdge (G : Graph) (e : Edge) (h : e ∉ G.E) : edgeCount (addEdge G e) = edgeCount G + 1`
#. §1: `edgeCount_addEdge`
#. §2: `edgeCount`
#. §3: `rw [edgeCount_addEdge]`
#. §4: `e ∉ G.E`
#. §5: `edgeCount_addEdge`
