#. §7: `rw [edgeCount_addEdge G e h]`
#. §8: `e ∉ G.E`
#: Game.Levels.GraphTheory.L03_Handshake
msgid "§0\n"
"\n"
"§1 is states that adding an edge to a graph increases its §2 (number of edges in the graph) by 1.\n"
"\n"
"## Important:\n"
"Doing just §3 forces you to prove §4 later as that assumption is an argument\n"
"for §5. If you already have §6 as a hypothesis, you can directly try\n"
"§7. Providing all the arguments here means you don't have prove\n"
"separately §8 later."
msgstr ""

